306195372.Title: Haier 24 in. 2.9 cu. ft. Electric Range with Self-Cleaning Convection Oven in Stainless Steel, Silver
306195372.Description: The Haier 2.9 cu. ft. Electric Range provides a convection cooking to meet all cooking needs. The ceramic smooth glass cooking surface provides a sleek appearance and is easy to clean. This versatile design gives you the option for a tradition look, or the ability to flip down to create a slide-in appearance. Color: Stainless Steel.

302692526.Title: Magic Chef 24 in. 2.2 cu. ft. Electric Range with Convection in Stainless Steel, Silver
302692526.Description: The Magic Chef 24 in. wide freestanding electric range is perfect for smaller spaces, yet lets you prepare family size meals. The programmable convection oven features seven cooking modes. Its 4-radiant element ceramic cooktop with a smooth surface allows for quick and easy cleaning. Its sleek stainless steel exterior complements any decor. Just like a full size range, there is a digital clock and timer, 2 oven racks, as well as anti-tilt bracket and adjustable legs.

204489380.Title: Summit Appliance 20 in. 2.5 cu. ft. Slide-In Electric Range in Stainless Steel, Silver
204489380.Description: Summit Professional brings luxury to apartment sized ranges with our exclusive line of 'slide-in' look ovens. The TEM110BRWY electric range is conveniently sized at just 20 in. wide to fit into even the tightest of kitchen spaces. Elegant stainless steel doors on the oven and lower storage compartment are matched with solid towel bar style handles. Our 'slide-in' units have a low stainless top frame that lets you customize the wall behind your range without planning around a backguard. A stainless steel manifold completes the modern look. Solidly constructed from black porcelain and steel, the TEM110BRWY is easy to clean and striking to view. The oven has a clear window and light so you can keep a watch on your cooking. Enjoy the best meals in unique style with lasting durability.

305572839.Title: Whirlpool 2.96 cu. ft. Single Oven Electric Range with Upswept Spill Guard Cooktop in Stainless Steel, Silver
305572839.Description: Serve up something for everyone, even in tight kitchens, with a small electric range. This stove meets the Standards for Accessible Design specified by the Americans with Disabilities Act and features an indicator light that lets you know when the oven is hot, even after it's been turned off. When messes happen, the porcelain-coated steel cooktop easily wipes clean. Color: Stainless Steel.

313973586.Title: Galanz 24 in. Electric Range in Stainless Steel 2.2 cu. ft. Oven, Silver
313973586.Description: The Galanz 24 in. wide, 2.2 cu. ft. radiant Range. This freestanding electric range with radiant cooktop is ideal for smaller spaces either in an apartment, cabin or just smaller kitchen. However, don't let the smaller width fool you it can still prepare family size meals. The 2200-Watt high output burner is ideal for searing at high heat but has the ability to change to a low simmer without moving the pot or pan. The European convection oven features several cooking modes to get outstanding results. It's 4 burner flush cooktop can accommodate different pan sizes. Galanz Appliances provide outstanding technology and great quality to bring you fantastic value in Kitchen appliances. With a modern sleek design, this suite of appliances is ideal for your family!. Color: Stainless Steel.

300052107.Description: The Premier 20 in.
